{
  "stem": "3605.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And even some of the Jewish policemen were-- if they did not behave right, they were also-- they were under sentence of death from the group.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If they denounced people or something, or certain Poles, that they denounced people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "These were-- It was ridiculous to say that we could undertake to fight the Germans as an army.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We didn't have enough resources.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We didn't have-- there wasn't enough [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] ammunition.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were just a few guns.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And what they did is make bombs, the Molotov cocktails or the other things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Even the people from the, later on, Warsaw ghetto uprising, were the nucleus of the [SPEAKING HEBREW]-- of the fighting-- halutz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were the people from one town to the other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That they got organized the best way they could.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, when my time came to go, I went.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I still cannot understand how my mother let me go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not only did-- did she let me go, she kind of pushed me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said, go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe you will survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I left my mother, brother, and grandmother, and I smuggled out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother gave me a little celluloid tube.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Needles used to be held in them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It-- it was-- you could close it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was the size of my finger, here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there she put some valuable stones that were in the family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And since we had contact with the drugstores, because they were buying medicine bottles from us, my brother could get me a poison pill.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what he gave me as a goodbye present.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Should I be caught, I shouldn't suffer too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the German was-- were known about their investigation and their beatings and their sadism, and so on-- that life was worse than death.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this is what I went out from.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
